data.description: Now Vacant and clean!! This home is on a huge corner lot fenced all around with white picket fence in front. Open floor plan, large dining area, hardwood flooring in living room, ceramic tile in kitchen and bathrooms, up to date fixtures in bath & kitchen with S/S appliances. Custom tile around the bathtub in the master bathroom. 5 min from hospital, 10 min from downtown tunnel. Room to add garage or in-law suite.
